org.openimaj.ml.clustering.assignment.hard

Class KDTreeIntEuclideanAssigner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.ml.clustering.assignment.hard.KDTreeIntEuclideanAssigner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assigner<int[]>, HardAssigner<int[],float[],IntFloatPair>

    public class KDTreeIntEuclideanAssigner
extends Object
implements HardAssigner<int[],float[],IntFloatPair>
    A HardAssigner that uses a IntNearestNeighboursKDTree to generate approximately correct cluster assignments.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
